# Cloudflare API credentials for DNS-01 challenge
# Copy this file to cloudflare.ini and fill with your token
#
# How to create the token:
# 1. Go to https://dash.cloudflare.com/profile/api-tokens
# 2. Click "Create Token"
# 3. Use template "Edit zone DNS" OR create custom:
#    - Permissions: Zone - DNS - Edit
#    - Zone Resources: Include - Specific zone - ayceventos.com.co
# 4. Copy the token here:

dns_cloudflare_api_token = YOUR_CLOUDFLARE_API_TOKEN_HERE